T7_Setup PHP editor

Sublime text - 
https://www.sublimetext.com/docs/linux_repositories.html#apt

Run below commands
==================
sudo apt-get install apt-transport-https

For Stable:- 
echo "deb https://download.sublimetext.com/ apt/stable/" | sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/sublime-text.list

For Developer:-
echo "deb https://download.sublimetext.com/ apt/dev/" | sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/sublime-text.list

sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install sublime-text

Eclipse PHP - 
https://www.eclipse.org/downloads/packages/release/2021-03/r/eclipse-ide-php-developers (Linux x86_64)

Run below commands
==================
https://www.journaldev.com/43780/install-eclipse-on-linux-mint
To install Snap use the command :

$ sudo apt update
$ sudo apt install snapd

Install Java
java -version 
sudo apt install default-jre 
sudo apt install default-jdk
sudo snap install eclipse --classic
snap info eclipse
eclipse